  <div id="db-doulist-section" class="indent">
    <ul class="bs">
          
            <li class=""><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/doulist/35785/" target="_blank">我知道这些书很怪但我爱的难以自拔</a>
                <span class="pl">(Josephine)</span>
            </li>
          
            <li class=""><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/doulist/16224/" target="_blank">曾改编成电影的书</a>
